0.3-0

o bug fixes.
o fixed error in url of package home page.
o Revised how model parameters are passed to the {{{ssa()}}} (per Ben Bolker's suggestion). Model parameters are now passed directly to {{{ssa()}}} as a named vector and hence they do not have to be declared in the global environment.

